    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于”狙击枪”套装</h2><br> 大距离狙击枪和强大手枪 —  任何狙击手必要的物品。拥有这些物品的战士一定不能输掉，也不用更改位置。胜利已经是你的！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700730/extras/622e0349fa9d8ba21fef94f3d00ebc0b.poster.avif?t=1685626293\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700730/extras/622e0349fa9d8ba21fef94f3d00ebc0b.webm?t=1685626293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700730/extras/622e0349fa9d8ba21fef94f3d00ebc0b.mp4?t=1685626293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br> 礼包中有强大的物品，玩家在任何条件下都能过获胜。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700730/extras/c18aedb5e075c18f1944c9209cbaf6fc.poster.avif?t=1685626293\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700730/extras/c18aedb5e075c18f1944c9209cbaf6fc.webm?t=1685626293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700730/extras/c18aedb5e075c18f1944c9209cbaf6fc.mp4?t=1685626293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>套装中有两把武器：合适任何职业（除了SED）的手枪，和“狙击枪”职业自动抢。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Desert Eagle</h2><br>尺寸巨大的导气式半自动手枪沙漠之鹰由美国马格纳斯研究所设计，主要由以色列军事工业公司负责制造。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700730/extras/f54527a3ae1f89c500fa6a6a2b4f4877.avif?t=1685626293\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AWM</h2>由战术前线国际公司生产的 武器是一款使用可拆卸的击步枪，同时也是第一款“狙击手专用”型号。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700730/extras/6d021555b2f192481793081b256bb8ed.avif?t=1685626293\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700730/extras/27a35f53c3549605771a418b5b2c82b2.avif?t=1685626293\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br>支付好之后请稍等15分钟左右。如果物品还没到账的话，请重新启动游戏。<br><br><strong>如果你得到了皇冠版本DesertEagle手枪，我们在不远的地方未来用普通版来代替它。非常抱歉带来的不便。</strong>",
